## Mandatory Design System Requirements

### 1. Colors - Use Design Tokens Only

**✅ REQUIRED:**
```tsx
// Text colors
<h1 className="text-primary">Heading</h1>
<p className="text-secondary">Body text</p>
<span className="text-accent">Accent text</span>
<h1 className="text-white">White text (on dark)</h1>
<p className="text-white/80">80% opacity white</p>

// Background colors
<section className="bg-primary">Dark section</section>
<section className="bg-surface">Light gray section</section>
<section className="bg-white">White section</section>
<div className="bg-accent/10">Accent tint</div>
```

**❌ FORBIDDEN:**
```tsx
<div className="text-gray-700">Bad</div>
<div className="bg-[#B8764F]">Bad</div>
<div className="text-blue-600">Bad</div>
```

### 2. Typography - Use Typography Scale Only

**✅ REQUIRED:**
```tsx
// Hero headlines (48px)
<h1 className="font-display text-hero text-white">Hero</h1>

// Page titles (36px)
<h1 className="font-display text-page-title text-primary">Page Title</h1>

// Section headings (28px)
<h2 className="font-display text-section text-primary">Section</h2>

// Subsections (20px)
<h3 className="font-display text-subsection text-primary">Subsection</h3>

// Body text
<p className="text-body-lg text-secondary">Large body</p>
<p className="text-body text-secondary">Standard body</p>
<span className="text-body-sm text-secondary">Small text</span>
<span className="text-caption text-accent">Caption</span>

// Responsive sizing
<h1 className="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-[4.5rem]">Responsive</h1>
```

**❌ FORBIDDEN:**
```tsx
<h1 className="text-[42px]">Bad</h1>
<p className="text-xl">Bad</p>
```

### 3. Eyebrow Text Pattern - Always Use

**✅ REQUIRED for section headers:**
```tsx
<span className="inline-block text-accent text-caption uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-semibold mb-4">
  Category Label
</span>
```

**Key properties:**
- `text-accent` - Bronze/copper color
- `text-caption` - 12px
- `uppercase` - All caps
- `tracking-[0.25em]` - Wide letter spacing
- `font-semibold` - 600 weight
- `mb-4` or `mb-6` - Space before heading

### 4. Section Headers - Centered Pattern

**✅ REQUIRED for section introductions:**
```tsx
<div className="text-center mb-16">
  <span className="inline-block text-accent text-caption uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-semibold mb-4">
    Eyebrow
  </span>
  <h2 className="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary leading-tight mb-6">
    Section Title
  </h2>
  <p className="text-body-lg text-secondary max-w-[42rem] mx-auto">
    Description text centered and constrained.
  </p>
</div>
```

### 5. Spacing - Use 8px System

**✅ REQUIRED:**
```tsx
// Section padding
<section className="py-20 md:py-28">Content</section>
<section className="py-10 md:py-12">Tight section</section>

// Component spacing
<div className="space-y-6">Stacked elements</div>
<div className="gap-8 lg:gap-12">Grid gaps</div>
<div className="mb-16">Bottom margin</div>
```

**❌ FORBIDDEN:**
```tsx
<div className="p-[18px]">Bad</div>
<div className="mt-3.5">Bad</div>
```

### 6. Container Widths

**✅ REQUIRED:**
```tsx
// Wide container (homepage, landing pages)
<div className="container-wide">Max 1440px</div>

// Standard container (most pages)
<div className="container-standard">Max 1280px</div>

// Prose container (long-form content)
<div className="container-prose">Max 640px</div>
```

### 7. Buttons on Dark Backgrounds

**✅ REQUIRED:**
```tsx
// Primary button (accent colored)
<Button variant="primary" className="!bg-accent !text-white !border-accent hover:!bg-accent/90">
  Primary CTA
</Button>

// Secondary button (white outline)
<Button variant="secondary" className="!border-white/30 !text-white hover:!bg-white/10">
  Secondary CTA
</Button>
```

### 8. Image Effects

**✅ REQUIRED for hero/featured images:**
```tsx
// Glow effect
<div className="relative">
  <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-accent/20 blur-3xl rounded-full scale-75" />
  <img src={image} className="relative drop-shadow-2xl" />
</div>

// Stat overlay on images
<div className="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 md:right-8 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-xl">
  <div className="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-accent">10K+</div>
  <p className="text-sm text-secondary">Description</p>
</div>
```

### 9. Grid Layouts

**✅ REQUIRED patterns:**
```tsx
// Two-column hero
<div className="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">

// Three-column showcase
<div className="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
  <div className="lg:col-span-3">Left</div>
  <div className="lg:col-span-6">Center</div>
  <div className="lg:col-span-3">Right</div>
</div>

// Trust bar
<div className="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-10">

// Testimonials
<div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

// Products grid
<div className="products-grid">
```

### 10. Focus States - All Interactive Elements

**✅ REQUIRED:**
```tsx
<button className="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-2">
  Button
</button>
```

### 11. Touch Targets - Minimum 44px

**✅ REQUIRED:**
```tsx
<button className="min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]">Tap target</button>
<Button size="lg">Large button meets target</Button>
```

