## Pre-Commit Checklist

Before committing any UI changes, verify:

- [ ] **Colors**: All colors use design tokens
- [ ] **Typography**: All text uses typography scale
- [ ] **Spacing**: All spacing uses 8px system
- [ ] **Eyebrows**: Section headers have eyebrow text
- [ ] **Containers**: Correct container width used
- [ ] **Focus States**: All interactive elements focusable
- [ ] **Touch Targets**: Minimum 44x44px
- [ ] **ARIA Labels**: Icon buttons have labels
- [ ] **Images**: Have aspect ratios set
- [ ] **Responsive**: Tested at mobile, tablet, desktop

