## Error Patterns - Must Fix

**"Arbitrary color detected"**
```tsx
// ❌ Wrong
<div className="text-gray-700">

// ✅ Fix
<div className="text-secondary">
```

**"Missing eyebrow text"**
```tsx
// ❌ Wrong - heading without eyebrow
<h2>Section Title</h2>

// ✅ Fix
<span className="inline-block text-accent text-caption uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-semibold mb-4">
  Label
</span>
<h2>Section Title</h2>
```

**"Button on dark without override"**
```tsx
// ❌ Wrong
<Button variant="primary">On dark background</Button>

// ✅ Fix
<Button variant="primary" className="!bg-accent !text-white">On dark</Button>
```

